Psagot Investment House Ltd. Key Developments

Apax Eyes IPO For Investment House Psagot 
Apr 3 17
Apax Partners (Israel) Ltd will reportedly seek to take Psagot Investment House Ltd. public in 2018 at a company valuation of 3.7 billion shekels. Reportedly, "The amount to be floated has not been decided yet. A prospectus has not yet been prepared,"


Psagot Investment House Ltd. Presents at The Tel Aviv Institutional Investment Conference, Mar-08-2016
Mar 5 16
Psagot Investment House Ltd. Presents at The Tel Aviv Institutional Investment Conference, Mar-08-2016. Venue: Tel Aviv Hilton, Avi, Israel. Presentation Date & Speakers: Mar-08-2016, Nir Moroz, CIO, Ori Greenfeld, Chief Economist & Strategist.


Gazit-Globe Receives Offers For Israel Holdings
Aug 9 15
Amot Investments Ltd. (TASE:AMOT) with Gindi Investments 1 Ltd., Big Shopping Centers, Ltd. (TASE:BIG) with Harel Insurance Investments & Financial Services Ltd (TASE:HARL) and Psagot Investment House Ltd. submitted an offer to acquire real-estate operations in Israel of Gazit-Globe, Ltd. (TASE:GZT). Gazit-Globe, Ltd. (TASE:GZT) also received offer from JTLV partnered with Menora Insurance, Clal Insurance Enterprises Holdings Ltd. (TASE:CLIS), and Amitim. Two international funds also lodged nonbinding bids. The deadline for binding bids will likely be set for October 2015.


